Hydrodessus
surinamensis

Young, 1970: 153; 
Spangler 1985
: 88; 

Bistroem
1988

: 37; 
Nilsson 2001
: 236.

The holotype (in Rijksmuseum van Natuurlijke Historie, Leiden, 
Young 1970
) was not examined, but nine paratypes (in FSCA) were, and the identity of this species is clear.
